Interface IOrderManager

All Known Implementing Classes:
OrderManager
public interface IOrderManager
The IOrderManager interface outlines the operations necessary for managing orders. This includes displaying new orders for a specific branch, processing orders, and viewing order details, with all methods potentially throwing IOException due to I/O operations.
